<br />\n貼幾張相出嚟冇頭冇尾咁做乜鳩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc343896ce34ecf0da729aa3a280e565ffe0522","tid":888104,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"就算前面有車頂住你都唔會踩上黃線啦<br />\n自己唔識留位？"},{"pid":"298b2355c85685738ec5f1268850351624bb22b0","tid":888104,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"上面講過唔過線既問題<br />\n有時啲路你預車流順住去咪一路慢慢跟住行<br />\n然後前面可能有啲車亂切線又拖慢左條龍<br />\n拖到你未過到就轉燈就要焗停黃線ga啦<br />\n唔通倒車向後移咩？旺區成日有呢啲情況ga啦"},{"pid":"409f604c056966bcc32333be2bf3ff37b1022f59","tid":888104,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0daf0af26d6b60852cb5df5ea7ad6a72741a9fd4","tid":888104,"uid":76747,"like":269,"dislike":23,"score":246,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"關你鳩事咩連登仔<br />\n報警你就報啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"多謝鼓勵 ！ 下次見到咁情況我都會照影照up!<br />\n再接再厲 多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係連登 同我鬥惡？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9111866666056a568b8f5ed479dbbc23e1e7f8db","tid":888104,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/04/183604_6d82079fb636f036f9a415ef19c228da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F04%2F183604_6d82079fb636f036f9a415ef19c228da.png&h=e8dcda92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/04/183606_56e0223785d3eba31f44946d5dae3125.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3